<template><AdminTablePage title="数据字典管理" desc="维护行业、城市、学历、专业、福利标签等基础字典" :list="list" :total="total" :loading="loading" :query="query" @load="load" @open="open"><template #toolbar><el-select v-model="query.dictType" clearable placeholder="字典类型" style="width:160px"><el-option label="行业" value="industry"/><el-option label="城市" value="city"/><el-option label="学历" value="education"/><el-option label="专业" value="major"/><el-option label="福利" value="welfare"/></el-select><el-button type="primary" @click="reload">查询</el-button></template><template #columns><el-table-column prop="dictType" label="类型" width="120"/><el-table-column prop="dictLabel" label="标签"/><el-table-column prop="dictValue" label="值"/><el-table-column prop="sort" label="排序" width="80"/></template><template #rowActions="{row}"><el-button text type="primary" @click="open(row)">编辑</el-button><el-button text type="danger" @click="del(row)">删除</el-button></template><template #dialogs><el-dialog v-model="dialog" title="字典项" width="460px"><el-form :model="form" label-width="80px"><el-form-item label="类型"><el-input v-model="form.dictType"/></el-form-item><el-form-item label="标签"><el-input v-model="form.dictLabel"/></el-form-item><el-form-item label="值"><el-input v-model="form.dictValue"/></el-form-item><el-form-item label="排序"><el-input-number v-model="form.sort" :min="0"/></el-form-item></el-form><template #footer><el-button @click="dialog=false">取消</el-button><el-button type="primary" @click="save">保存</el-button></template></el-dialog></template></AdminTablePage></template><script setup>import{reactive,ref,onMounted}from'vue';import{ElMessage,ElMessageBox}from'element-plus';import AdminTablePage from '@/components/AdminTablePage.vue';import{adminApi}from'@/api';const query=reactive({pageNum:1,pageSize:10,dictType:''});const list=ref([]),total=ref(0),loading=ref(false),dialog=ref(false);const form=reactive({});const load=async()=>{loading.value=true;try{const p={...query};if(!p.dictType)delete p.dictType;const r=await adminApi.dicts(p);list.value=r.data.records;total.value=Number(r.data.total)}finally{loading.value=false}};const reload=()=>{query.pageNum=1;load()};const open=row=>{Object.keys(form).forEach(k=>delete form[k]);Object.assign(form,row||{sort:0});dialog.value=true};const save=async()=>{await adminApi.saveDict(form);ElMessage.success('保存成功');dialog.value=false;load()};const del=row=>ElMessageBox.confirm('确定删除该字典项？').then(async()=>{await adminApi.delDict(row.id);load()});onMounted(load)</script>